cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.HC 

The paper deals with the segmentation of the hippocampus from MRI scans, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The authors also use statistical analysis and machine learning techniques to evaluate the segmentation methods, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper deals with the application of the segmentation method in epilepsy patients, which could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
